2ee5f3ac660e5f34d7d03ff33f633d810428129030074d6b9ee84831045f99f5230c5a6d6da493c1dcb42311ccbfd993abeccbded28caebf002b8f9d5cb52f95  fix-aggregate-float-out.patch
